com.google.ical.iter
Interface RecurrenceIterator

All Superinterfaces:
java.util.Iterator<DateValue>
public interface RecurrenceIterator
extends java.util.Iterator<DateValue>

an iterator over date values in order. Does not support the remove operation.

mikesamuel+svn@gmail.com (Mike Samuel)
